     </div>
     <div class="footnote"><a class="note-ref" href="#PJA04d079n2-ptr" id="PJA04d079n2">2</a>
      
   <p><span class="ref-st" title="fade=[ on ] fadespeed=[0.1] windowlock=[on] cssbody=[ boxover ] header=[]  body=[ &lt;i&gt;Journals of the House of Representatives of Massachusetts&lt;/i&gt; [[1715-]], Boston, reprinted by the Massachusetts Historical Society, 1919-. (For the years for which reprints are not yet available, the original printings are cited, by year and session.) ]">Mass., <span class="hi-italic" style="font-style: italic;">House Jour.</span></span>, 17751776, 4th sess., p. 16. The House received the Councils message on 16 March and appointed a committee of three to consider it, but the journal records no further action.</p>

